Yay, can anyone here remove that black background from the above button and add the 4 colors from the Microsoft logo? <br /><br />I'd like also to see in all the 3 steps the official colors, not white to blue, with that same glossy effect. <br /><br />So, remove black background, logo with official colors and no changes, same glossy effect. Thanks in advance! <br /><br />I mean this logo: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://th03.deviantart.net/fs70/PRE/f/2012/312/7/3/microsoft___windows_8_logo_by_n_studios_2-d5keldy.png">http://th03.deviantart.net/fs70/PRE/f/2 ... 5keldy.png</a><!-- m --> <br /><br />I've tried already that one, it's really cool, but I wanna have the original effect and colors (red, green, blue and yellow). The original goes like this: <br /><br />1. White W8 logo, no colored background (transparent). <br /><br />2. When you hover the mouse over it, the background changes to black (which is really ugly), the W8 logo changes to the color you've selected in Settings/Personalize/Accent color in Start Screen METRO. And then there's a shinny effect, like a gloss. <br /><br />3. Once you click it, nothing changes, same black background color, same accent colored W8 logo, no extra effect. <br /><br />What I want is: <br /><br />1. Same design and size W8 logo, but with official colors: red, green, blue and yellow. Transparent background of course. <br /><br />2. When you hover the mouse over it, the background is still transparent, the logo has the same colors. The only thing that happens is the glass effect. <br /><br />3. Once you click it, nothing changes. (well, you could do 2 versions: a original version in which nothing changes after the click, and a second version, in which when you click the start button, it gets a little smaller or something like that, not too exaggerated/extravagant, just a little tweak so we know it's clicked) <br /><br />Many thanks, hope it's not too difficult.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2514">rambomhtri</a> — Tue Jun 10, 2014 10:58 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
